note for ReportSpec "DB: Jobs has ReportSpecID (FK)<br/>Domain (new): Report -&gt; ReportSpec"

note for Report "DB: Report key is (JobID, ReportNr) and FK to Job<br/>Domain: Report belongs to Cylinder<br/><br/>Mapping resolved in application layer"
